title: Barmer (Rajasthan Assembly constituency)
text:
Barmer Legislative Assembly constituency is one of the 200 <a href="Rajasthan%20Legislative%20Assembly">Legislative Assembly</a> constituencies of <a href="Rajasthan">Rajasthan</a> state in <a href="India">India</a>.
It is part of <a href="Barmer%20district">Barmer</a> district.
